"For 3D math, Godot provides a :ref:`Plane <class_Plane>` built-in type that "
"handles this."
msgstr ""
"3D演算の場合、Godotはこれを処理する組み込み型 :ref:`Plane <class_Plane>` を提"
"供します。"

